full_text: The last Blackhawks win at Chicago Stadium. Gary Suter with a hat trick, and JR goes backdoor on Felix Potvin to tie the Western Conference Quarterfinals at 2-2 to ensure one more game was going to be played on Stadium ice. It ended with a series-ending 1-0 shutout for the Leafs. https://t.co/M4Nu5bGaGR
